00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:47.000
 We could not have chosen a better city than Paris to present a prototype that embodies the promise of Akio Toyoda 

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.000
 to build cars that excite and make you love driving. 

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:58.000
 The C-HR prototype exteriors win in many respects. 

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:10.000
 The faceted surfaces recall the shape of a diamond and give the car a fluid and sinuous line, anticipating the stylistic language of the future Toyota models. 

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:19.000
