00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:41.000
 combined with the low, wide and massive shape of the wheel arches, it anticipates the design of future Toyota cars. 

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:48.000
 This car will certainly not go unnoticed, also thanks to the exclusive design of the alloy wheels that will emphasize its presence on the road. 

00:01:49.000 --> 00:02:02.000
 And behind the bold exterior, you'll find an advanced version of our integral hybrid transmission. In addition, thanks to a new platform that allows better handling, dynamic driving is guaranteed. 

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:09.000
